00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:37.920
[Amit Varma]: And we respect the institution we regard as the guardian of that constitution, the Supreme

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:38.920
[Amit Varma]: Court.

00:00:38.920 --> 00:00:42.600
[Amit Varma]: There might be many things wrong with our society and our culture, but we think of the

00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:46.680
[Amit Varma]: Supreme Court as the one institution that can mitigate them.

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:52.200
[Amit Varma]: But what if, instead of mitigating the faults of society, the Supreme Court instead reflects

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:55.160
[Amit Varma]: them and even deepens them?

00:00:55.160 --> 00:01:11.640
[Unknown]: What are we to do then?

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:16.120
